# Web3Forms access key for contact + open-house form submissions.
# Sign up at https://web3forms.com (free, no card required) and paste the
# key here for local dev, or set it in the Vercel project env vars for prod.
# When this is unset, form submissions return a Web3Forms error and the
# inline error state is shown to the user.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=
